Company comment:
The patient is a 58-year-old male prescribed Acthar on 02OCT2014 for the treatment of membranous nephropathy.
No additional medical history or concomitant medications were provided. On (b) (6) , a report was received 
that the patient was hospitalized for infected colitis and had an elevated white blood cell count. The patient also 
